description: Structure complex frontend views with thin containers and composed view-model hooks
alwaysApply: true
---

# Complex View Architecture Pattern

- Keep top-level `*View.tsx` files thin; move behavior into composed `use*ViewModel` hooks.
- Decompose large tabs/pages by section panels into focused components.
- Pass grouped, typed models between container/tabs/sections; avoid long flat prop lists.
- Place feature files under `frontend/src/views/<feature>/...` and prefer shared styles/utilities before local one-offs.
- Preserve existing UX behavior unless explicitly requested to change it.
